    rm(res)
}

for(iker in 1:5){
    load(paste0(workdir,"/output/",sample[isam],"_",itype,"_everyother_gaus",iker,"_kdc.rds"))
    single_per_pval <- cbind(single_per_pval,res$pval)
    rm(res)
}
load(paste0(workdir,"/output/",sample[isam],"_",itype,"_Projection_kdc.rds"))
single_per_pval <- cbind(single_per_pval,res$pval)
genes           <- rownames(res)
rm(res)
combined_pvals  <- CombinePValues(single_per_pval)
names(combined_pvals) <- genes
pBY     <- p.adjust(na.omit(combined_pvals),method="BY")
pBY_proj <- p.adjust(na.omit(single_per_pval[,11]),method="BY")
pBY_5x          <- pBY
comb_pvals_5x   <- combined_pvals

# shared genes
rm(list=setdiff(ls(),c("pBY_5x","comb_pvals_5x","isam")))

sample = c("CN13_D2","CN24_D1","CN24_E1","CN21_E2","CN21_C1","CN21_D1")
itype = "HDST"
load(paste0(workdir,"/data/",sample[isam],"_unmodgtf_filtered_red_ut_",itype,"_final.rds"))
single_per_pval <- c()
for(iker in 1:5){
    load(paste0(workdir,"/output/",sample[isam],"_",itype,"_everyother_cosine",iker,"_kdc.rds"))
    single_per_pval <- cbind(single_per_pval,res$pval)
    rm(res)
}

for(iker in 1:5){
    load(paste0(workdir,"/output/",sample[isam],"_",itype,"_everyother_gaus",iker,"_kdc.rds"))
    single_per_pval <- cbind(single_per_pval,res$pval)
    rm(res)
}

load(paste0(workdir,"/output/",sample[isam],"_",itype,"_Projection_kdc.rds"))
single_per_pval <- cbind(single_per_pval,res$pval)
genes           <- rownames(res)
rm(res)
combined_pvals  <- CombinePValues(single_per_pval)
names(combined_pvals) <- genes
pBY     <- p.adjust(na.omit(combined_pvals),method="BY")
pBY_proj <- p.adjust(na.omit(single_per_pval[,11]),method="BY")

pBY_hdst            <- pBY
comb_pvals_hdst     <- combined_pvals

diff_gene       <- union(setdiff(names(pBY_5x),names(pBY_hdst)),setdiff(names(pBY_hdst),names(pBY_5x)))
shared_gene     <- intersect(names(pBY_hdst[pBY_hdst<0.05]),names(pBY_5x[pBY_5x<0.05]))
hdst_over_5x    <- setdiff(names(pBY_hdst[pBY_hdst<0.05]),names(pBY_5x[pBY_5x<0.05]))
x5_over_hdst    <- setdiff(setdiff(names(pBY_5x[pBY_5x<0.05]),names(pBY_hdst[pBY_hdst<0.05])),diff_gene)

topgenes_x5     <- names(sort(comb_pvals_5x[x5_over_hdst]))
topgenes_shared <- names(sort(comb_pvals_5x[shared_gene]))

selected_x5     <- head(topgenes_x5,10)
selected_hdst   <- head(topgenes_shared,10)

# 5x genes
rm(list=setdiff(ls(),c("selected_hdst","selected_x5","isam")))
library(Rcpp)

source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/freq_func.R")
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/simple_plot.R")

sample = c("CN13_D2","CN24_D1","CN24_E1","CN21_E2","CN21_C1","CN21_D1")

load(paste0("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/kdc/experiment/realdata/hdst/data/",sample[isam],"_unmodgtf_filtered_red_ut_HDST_final.rds"))

sp_hdst     <- sp_count
loc_hdst    <- location

rm(sp_count,location)

load(paste0("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/kdc/experiment/realdata/hdst/data/",sample[isam],"_unmodgtf_filtered_red_ut_5x_final.rds"))

sp_5x   <- sp_count
loc_5x  <- location
rm(sp_count,location)

ct_hdst     <- log(sp_hdst[selected_hdst,]+1)
ct_5x       <- log(sp_5x[selected_hdst,]+1)

ct_hdst_rel <- apply(ct_hdst,1,relative_func)
ct_5x_rel   <- apply(ct_5x,1,relative_func)

pltdat_hdst  <- cbind.data.frame(loc_hdst[,1:2],ct_hdst_rel)
pltdat_5x  <- cbind.data.frame(loc_5x[,1:2],ct_5x_rel)

colnames(pltdat_hdst) <- c("x","y",paste0(selected_hdst,"_HDST"))
colnames(pltdat_5x) <- c("x","y",paste0(selected_hdst,"_5X"))

pp_hdst      <- lapply(1:(ncol(pltdat_hdst)-2),function(x){pattern_plot3_italic(pltdat_hdst,x,main=T,pointsize=1,titlesize=1,min.pand=0.8,max.pand=1.01)})

pp_5x      <- lapply(1:(ncol(pltdat_5x)-2),function(x){pattern_plot3_italic(pltdat_5x,x,main=T,pointsize=2,titlesize=1,min.pand=0.8,max.pand=1.01)})

library(ggpubr)
fig1    <- ggarrange(pp_hdst[[1]],pp_hdst[[2]],pp_hdst[[3]],
                    pp_hdst[[4]],pp_hdst[[5]],pp_hdst[[6]],
                    pp_hdst[[7]],pp_hdst[[8]],pp_hdst[[9]],
                    ncol = 3, nrow = 3)

fig2    <- ggarrange(pp_5x[[1]],pp_5x[[2]],pp_5x[[3]],
                    pp_5x[[4]],pp_5x[[5]],pp_5x[[6]],
                    pp_5x[[7]],pp_5x[[8]],pp_5x[[9]],
                    ncol = 3, nrow = 3)
